[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring logging features**\n\nI’m considering testing the Slf4jLogMarker and LoggingAdapter with markers, especially since Akka 2.6 supports LogMarker publicly. It seems existing tests don't cover markers, which is a functional feature of akka-slf4j that preserves SLF4J markers through the event bus. \n\nThough it's tricky to test without a backend, I could call Slf4jLoggingFilter's marker overloads and Logger. Maybe I can use the MarkerFactory to assert on marker identity without duplication. A test for the logging adapter supporting markers might be worth writing too!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0ce37203789b38590169fabe45f9ac81a2a9f76a1c6fe5cea2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-r5JqPrmZwc6DZA8zfkMjIAEvhKa9vdczNRYimktAVeSTuyHR6Kc7JBOq60aA_zU2FL_ko5ILY9WfzPBHZ-GntIJm6aJ0DARBPT4BaZQueY118bpEsEdP_y65tyr3tltKwkWKcf3N8D-hpb0wD_Fou3zpsFBGKx4OLNVwOOeK8zPfSNh_oCqsqbS03v7UUNHoAktEs_gpK3ttLidLxHJkOPTpWygwapU6Kr7e2lnCeVVIEo81TaQAejeQF2hOLlrz6vskEeHHMwAsvM88EBxDTe0hjNEXTFjTHgSazutI7XdHsfEuu_06HIKlkBqhFB3PDwtLeeYv0J0RFoiHCjDHaqZvv4PBHvHeS_w9P1CxnCfjhIVRa6-5D0xieixPEg7U1lDs2PxzW7f5HIIVSf3yqgSb_qeeFHWygGkeP85AMMgWQEkAqP8V6n3rPrBFvu7zUHE0ir6v8glSx8kTaBXT8eoYue7jhyEZidbeZLReeQIZ6ZFM1VizRB7xQS39W8J3GJ43VTqN_DqkiXLbRAH3qRJ7YI-UQTBKomW-K624XxEucXkzGkb8jYzDh69Yh_FLLnUL4cKOQpVp_Q32WPka-3XenVw-2QHkE7kEp6pnlGEg2YeOWhRPhn5biD9TLWxMIYXX4HG7wL-wXWRtJyrAB8E0qzmTH4T_GZzdXELPuAzKEyJPW2w2k2QtCLFHgY3fyC9KBWKqG7uTT-KZrGwU35yDLCXfmum-1Ko4hESl49ImVKI40sZTHPo9-JbReWYidQ4OPOTDC5lvamzBnEJJeOooC7c7FUaFYbwDNu0R-VUx2TVRMbbzm5tCWjRZTgQqK_-s1GETVj7dLUXpgRJ5uSXda6EtK-hvDjjW0QC0ATl38jXAdyEjBWm9VSDQxC7_bbxxDe7lNmEF5Ak0fiAlgzdziLG5oUvEJp6_k-z_cQj0QAhTc3HZOR29JGYtgwuv_3EmP6KQKMT65h-TUPoicJ1j67Mfo6NMt6jBgxu0VLHuiVOBobxqe8RxdsTykK-o5N0Rg4CKiKdKLeB9BPuFbhuiPY9aozgoTOTLd6x9pXOL6td7k06DB98woe9U3vhzMBvuV1tOVLzqh9Bp6mE6xQ-KBjPM9hyvqLeKcN-OO_NYeADJz4vyAkNxy6oe9vrghTxk4L2wO4K